GLOBAL UI FRAMEWORK (ALL ROLES — SYSTEM OF PROOF)
Application Shell (Persistent for All Authenticated Roles)
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│ Top Bar                                                  │
│ Org Name | Active Role | Alerts | Evidence Status | User │
├───────────────┬─────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ Left Nav      │ Main Content Area                        │
│ (Role-Based)  │ Evidence-Driven, Immutable Views         │
└───────────────┴─────────────────────────────────────────┘

Universal UI Rules (ABSOLUTE)

❌ No edit icons on historical records

❌ No delete actions on regulated data

❌ No overwrite of evidence

✅ Status badges are system-derived and immutable

✅ Evidence links are always visible when present

✅ Every screen shows “Last Evaluated At”

✅ All AI outputs are explicitly labeled “Advisory (Non-Authoritative)”

✅ Any blocked action is visually disabled AND server-enforced

❌ No UI-only enforcement

